1019505/iraqi-refugees-leading-an-uncertain-life|title=Iraqi refugees \u2013 leading an uncertain life|work=Dawn|date=20 June 2013|accessdate=9 October 2014}}</ref> || [[Kurds in Pakistan]]\n|-\n| {{flag|Tajikistan}} || {{nts|7}} <small>(2010 census)</small><ref>{{cite web|script-title=ru:\u041d\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0441\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432, \u0432\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u044f\u0437\u044b\u043a\u0430\u043c\u0438 \u0438 \u0433\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043d\u0430\u0441\u0435\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u0440\u0435\u0441\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0438 \u0442\u0430\u0434\u0436\u0438\u043a\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d|url=http://www.stat.tj/en/img/526b8592e834fcaaccec26a22965ea2b_1355502192.pdf|work=Statistics of Tajikistan|publisher=Statistics of Tajikistan|accessdate=27 January 2013|page=9|language=Russian, Tajik|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116004155/http://stat.tj/en/img/526b8592e834fcaaccec26a22965ea2b_1355502192.pdf|archive-date=2013-01-16|url-status=dead}}</ref> ||  {{Pct |7 | 7564502| 1 }}  || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n|}\n\n===Americas and Oceania===\n[[File:US states with a Kurdish population with over 1000.svg|thumb|200px|right|American states with a Kurdish population of over 1,000 (ACS 2011-2015)]]\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width: 75%; height: 14em;\"\n|-\n! [[List of sovereign states|Country]] !! Official figures  !! Official figures in % !! Further information\n|-\n| {{flag|United States}} || {{nts|20,591}} <small>(2011-2015 [[American Community Survey|ACS]])</small><ref name=\"usa\">{{cite web|title=2011-2015 American Community Survey Selected Population Tables|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_10_SF4_B01003&prodType=table|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200212214434/http://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?p