c_89.php?reg=13 |date=2012-01-04 }}. ''Demoscope.ru''</ref><br>{{nts|37,470}} <small>([[Census in Armenia|2011 census]]){{ref|Armenia number|d}}</small>  || {{Pct |56127 | 3304776| 1 }}<br>{{Pct |37470 | 3018854| 1 }}  || [[Kurds in Armenia]]\n{| class=\"collapsible collapsed\" style=\"width:100%; font-size:88%; border-top:#aaa 1px solid;\"\n|-\n![[Provinces of Armenia|Provinces]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Armenia ethnicity 2011|url=http://pop-stat.mashke.org/armenia-ethnic2011.htm}}</ref>\n!(2011)\n|-\n|[[Armavir Province]]||17,063<ref>{{cite web|script-title=hy:\u0540\u0540 \u0531\u0580\u0574\u0561\u057e\u056b\u0580\u056b \u0574\u0561\u0580\u0566, \u0574\u0577\u057f\u0561\u056f\u0561\u0576 \u0562\u0576\u0561\u056f\u0579\u0578\u0582\u0569\u0575\u0578\u0582\u0576|url=http://armstat.am/file/doc/99481488.pdf|work=Statistics of Armenia|publisher=Statistics of Armenia|accessdate=27 May 2014|language=Armenian}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Aragatsotn Province]]||7,090<ref>{{cite web|script-title=hy:\u0540\u0540 \u0531\u0580\u0561\u0563\u0561\u056e\u0578\u057f\u0576\u056b \u0574\u0561\u0580\u0566, \u0574\u0577\u057f\u0561\u056f\u0561\u0576 \u0562\u0576\u0561\u056f\u0579\u0578\u0582\u0569\u0575\u0578\u0582\u0576|url=http://armstat.am/file/doc/99480788.pdf|work=Statistics of Armenia|publisher=Statistics of Armenia|accessdate=27 May 2014|language=Armenian}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Ararat Province]]||5,001<ref>{{cite web|script-title=hy:\u0540\u0540 \u0531\u0580\u0561\u0580\u0561\u057f\u056b \u0574\u0561\u0580\u0566, \u0574\u0577\u057f\u0561\u056f\u0561\u0576 \u0562\u0576\u0561\u056f\u0579\u0578\u0582\u0569\u0575\u0578\u0582\u0576\u056b|url=http://armstat.am/file/doc/99481128.pdf|work=Statistics of Armenia|publisher=Statistics of Armenia|accessdate=27 May 2014|language=Armenian}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Yerevan]]||3,361<ref>{{cite web|script-title=hy:\u0584. \u0535\u0580\u0587\u0561\u0576, \u0574\u0577\u057f\u0561\u056f\u0561\u0576 \u0562\u0576\u0561\u056f\u0579\u0578\u0582\u0569\u0575\u0578\u0582\u0576|url=http://